Shotgun is the application that opens the doors of electronic nights to you (techno, house, acid, minimal, micro, etc.): 

* Discover a selection of parties based on your musical tastes;
* Buy your tickets for the best festivals, clubs, afters and of course alternative warehouse parties;
* Resell your tickets easily if you change your mind;
* Give tickets to your friends;
* Find also in the app your tickets bought on the Shotgun website (by logging in with the same IDs)


______________________________

In US, France, Portugal, Spain, UK and Brazil,  Shotgun is the application that guides you in your electronic outings, that uncovers for you all the thriving nightlife and makes it accessible. 
